{"tid":2272340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官斥士沙瞞真相 技工脫罪","createTime":"2020-11-05T04:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T04:43:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"21820dfe99b18be56bf76a9d8282650234bcc348","tid":2272340,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/XIS6YZQAWJF6LIWPCHXUGSRZIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FXIS6YZQAWJF6LIWPCHXUGSRZIU%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4DH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=10b04edc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FXIS6YZQAWJF6LIWPCHXUGSRZIU%2F&h=0909c797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/XIS6YZQAWJF6LIWPCHXUGSRZIU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n官斥士沙瞞真相 技工脫罪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年聖誕節市民在多區商場響應「和你Shop」行動，自稱當晚在九龍灣德福廣場穿戴防暴裝備「高調巡邏」的警署警長（士沙）。。。。。。。。。。，裁定他罪脫兼得訟費，並批評警署警長看片後仍不說出實情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7EA6Cf9vD26dQn9-b7jSDN6wC6o=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VE7ZXOELZVHKDCG2PDLH7BCY3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7EA6Cf9vD26dQn9-b7jSDN6wC6o%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVE7ZXOELZVHKDCG2PDLH7BCY3Y.jpg&h=fbe230fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警署警長張基耀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片證踩人在先<br />\n<br />\n控罪原指被告黃浩峰（24歲）去年12月25日在德福一期襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員，即警署警長33320張基耀，被告昨於觀塘法院脫罪時，庭內掌聲如雷。裁判官梁少玲昨裁決指，呈堂兩段立場新聞及香港電台片段，均清晰顯示被告被捕前，未有如張稱向前踏步推撞，反而拍到是張先踩被告及用肩膊撞被告，不能排除被告因自然反應而推開張。<br />\n<br />\n梁官批評，張起初的書面口供並無提過被告踏前，庭上證供亦與新聞片段明顯不脗合，他作供時即使觀看新聞片段及截圖後，仍未有說出真相，堅稱。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n早前審訊時，張供稱當日被告突然踏前一步，迎面用右半身撞他左邊膊頭，令他身體向橫移動。惟辯方播放新聞片段，指張當日取道經過現場時，身邊仍有不少空位，卻偏偏走近被告身旁，並先用左腳踩被告右腳，繼而用左膊撞被告右膊，再喊襲警。辯方直斥張「賊喊捉賊」，張激動否認，指辯方說法屬虛構，堅稱「我冇踢過、冇掂過、冇踩過佢隻腳，冇任何身體接觸。」<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTCC1056/20"},{"pid":"076052d2df0849fff0d2cdc0caace09b6f9a9a96","tid":2272340,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:16:57.000Z","msg":"俾鬼撞"},{"pid":"709a0a84886398175a197e3daceddf775570ffaf","tid":2272340,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de71e2bfaa0e3f7b0e5776063f8a55b6bb2465f","tid":2272340,"uid":283700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"其實有無得要求佢驗係咪精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1886ef93e67261b5c6499abe5f5dd3c0b33bcd59","tid":2272340,"uid":47042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:19:39.000Z","msg":"有無原片？"},{"pid":"50f815b56b16043d639e8f224b6e026934dcc9f4","tid":2272340,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:19:39.000Z","msg":"黑"},{"pid":"b8d1cd3fd09f072726207b37f0aca8ceba92a76e","tid":2272340,"uid":42355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"比假口供又係冇後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441c926ec05698f851aa9d19b87d45982c6587c4","tid":2272340,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8de71e2bfaa0e3f7b0e5776063f8a55b6bb2465f","tid":2272340,"uid":283700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"其實有無得要求佢驗係咪精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"咁要狗隊集體去驗先得"},{"pid":"e0cc32f2fe771efaa13215d136063e317cade3b6","tid":2272340,"uid":33500